body_html:
I see, you are calling runInference() twice? You should only need to call it once, even if you're reading from two output nodes. Though it shouldn't crash if you do.

There's nothing at all beyond the SIGSEGV line? That is surprising -- are you sure you're not filtering it out somehow?
